query:
SELECT e.id, e.evaluation_date, e.gp_name, e.team_id
FROM evaluations e
WHERE e.team_id = (SELECT id FROM fm_teams WHERE name = 'Team Alpha' LIMIT 1)
ORDER BY e.evaluation_date DESC
LIMIT 10;
